{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/fate-series-dari-game-pc-hingga-meraih-popularitas-di-smartphone/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Fate Series: Dari Game PC Hingga Meraih Popularitas Di Smartphone","content":"<p>Fate series. Sebenarnya game apa ini?</p>\n<p>Well, jika melihat dari asal muasalnya, Fate series dimulai dari game ‘adult visual novel’ yang berjudul “Fate/Stay Night”, di rilis tahun 2004 (di-remaster tahun 2007 dengan judul “Fate/Stay Night: Réalta Nua” disertai sejumlah penambahan elemen seperti voice acting) untuk platform PC.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_14595\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-14595\" data-attachment-id=\"14595\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/fate-series-dari-game-pc-hingga-meraih-popularitas-di-smartphone/attachment/11-33/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/11-7.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Cover adult visual novel game Fate/Stay Night. Sumber gambar: wikipedia.org\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Cover adult visual novel game Fate/Stay Night. Sumber gambar: wikipedia.org&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/11-7.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/11-7.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-14595 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/11-7.jpg\" alt=\"Fate series fate/stay night\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-14595\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Cover adult visual novel game Fate/Stay Night. Sumber gambar: wikipedia.org</p></div></p>\n<p>Ide dasar game ini berasal dari sebuah event yang disebut “Holy Grail Wars”. Event ini melibatkan tujuh orang Magi, atau praktisi sihir (dalam game disebut ‘Master’) bersama asisten mereka (disebut ‘Servant’).  Yang menarik bukan hanya tentang Holy Grail yang bisa mengabulkan segala permintaan, tapi juga sosok para Servant dari Master tersebut.</p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kinoko-nasu-sosok-di-balik-kemisteriusan-dunia-dalam-visual-novel-fate-stay-night-dan-light-novel-kara-no-kyoukai/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Kinoko Nasu, Sosok di Balik Kemisteriusan Dunia dalam Visual Novel Fate/Stay Night dan Light Novel Kara no Kyoukai</a></strong></p>\n<p>Para Servant merupakan reinkarnasi ataupun hasil summon/materialisasi dari tokoh-tokoh penting dalam sejarah peradaban manusia. Tak hanya manusia, tokoh-tokoh sejarah seperti King Arthur atau Jeanne D’Arc, tokoh mitologi klasik seperti Hercules dan Medusa pun ada disini. Dan sepanjang cerita bergulir, tokoh-tokoh ini akan berperang demi memperebutkan Holy Grail.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_14589\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-14589\" data-attachment-id=\"14589\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/fate-series-dari-game-pc-hingga-meraih-popularitas-di-smartphone/attachment/9-44/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/9-12.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"“King Arthur of Great Britain” di versi game Fate. Sumber gambar: fategrandorder.wikia.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;“King Arthur of Great Britain” di versi game Fate. Sumber gambar: fategrandorder.wikia.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/9-12.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/9-12.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-14589 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/9-12.jpg\" alt=\"Fate series arturia\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-14589\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">“King Arthur of Great Britain” di versi game Fate. Sumber gambar: fategrandorder.wikia.com</p></div></p>\n<p>Fate series mengalami perubahan serta evolusi <em>gameplay</em> seiring berjalannya waktu. Awalnya Fate/Stay Night dibuat dalam bentuk visual novel dengan elemen “fan service” yang lumayan dominan. Jangan mainin game-nya kalau belum berusia 18+ yah, bro sis. hehe</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_14574\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-14574\" data-attachment-id=\"14574\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/fate-series-dari-game-pc-hingga-meraih-popularitas-di-smartphone/attachment/4-120/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/4-24.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Fate/Stay Night: Réalta Nua ‘hehe’ scene. Sumber gambar: imgur.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Fate/Stay Night: Réalta Nua ‘hehe’ scene. Sumber gambar: imgur.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/4-24.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/4-24.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-14574 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/4-24.jpg\" alt=\"Fate series tohsaka rin\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-14574\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Fate/Stay Night: Réalta Nua ‘hehe’ scene. Sumber gambar: imgur.com</p></div></p>\n<p>Namun game-game berikutnya dari Fate series mulai meninggalkan elemen ‘dewasa’ yang sebelumnya ada di ‘adult visual novel’ lalu. Kali ini, Fate lebih fokus ke genre petualangan dan aksi seru di Holy Grail Wars antar para Masters dengan Servants mereka.</p>\n<p>Dan tidak hanya di PC, serial game Fate mulai merambah ke berbagai platform video game. Handheld dan console juga ikut diramaikan dengan berbagai jenis game Fate series. Misalnya game “Fate/Extra” untuk handheld Sony PlayStation Portable atau “Fate/Unlimited Codes” untuk console Sony PlayStation 2. Kedua game ber-genre fighting ini berisikan tokoh-tokoh populer dari Fate series seperti Saber dan Gilgamesh.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_14586\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-14586\" data-attachment-id=\"14586\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/fate-series-dari-game-pc-hingga-meraih-popularitas-di-smartphone/attachment/8-53/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/8-13.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Fate/Extra untuk PSP. Sumber gambar: wikipedia.org\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Fate/Extra untuk PSP. Sumber gambar: wikipedia.org&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/8-13.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/8-13.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-14586 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/8-13.jpg\" alt=\"Fate series fate/extra\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-14586\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Fate/Extra untuk PSP. Sumber gambar: wikipedia.org</p></div></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_14571\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-14571\" data-attachment-id=\"14571\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/fate-series-dari-game-pc-hingga-meraih-popularitas-di-smartphone/attachment/3-129/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/3-24.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Screenshot game Fate/Unlimited Codes. Sumber gambar: emuparadise.meScreenshot game Fate/Unlimited Codes. Sumber gambar: emuparadise.me\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Screenshot game Fate/Unlimited Codes. Sumber gambar: emuparadise.me&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/3-24.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/3-24.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-14571 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/3-24.jpg\" alt=\"Fate series fate/unlimited codes\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-14571\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Screenshot game Fate/Unlimited Codes. Sumber gambar: emuparadise.me</p></div></p>\n<h2>Game Fate Series Paling Populer di Smartphone</h2>\n<p>Tapi sepertinya game Fate untuk smartphone lebih populer dibanding versi lainnya, yaitu “Fate/Grand Order” yang tersedia untuk platform Android &amp; iOS.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_14577\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-14577\" data-attachment-id=\"14577\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/fate-series-dari-game-pc-hingga-meraih-popularitas-di-smartphone/attachment/5-111/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/5-28.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Title screen FGO game. Sumber gambar: youtube.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Title screen FGO game. Sumber gambar: youtube.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/5-28.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/5-28.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-14577 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/5-28.jpg\" alt=\"Fate series fate/grand order\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-14577\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Title screen FGO game. Sumber gambar: youtube.com</p></div></p>\n<p>Mengapa FGO sangat populer saat ini? Alasannya ada beberapa.</p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/tahun-baru-fate-grand-order-jepang-juga-siapkan-season-baru/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Tahun Baru, Fate/Grand Order Jepang juga Siapkan Season Baru!</a></strong></p>\n<p>Misalnya karena platform yang digunakan. Saat ini smartphone bro sis mempermudah memainkan game kapanpun dan dimana saja.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_14580\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-14580\" data-attachment-id=\"14580\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/fate-series-dari-game-pc-hingga-meraih-popularitas-di-smartphone/attachment/6-85/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/6-22.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Promotional poster FGO game. Sumber gambar: twitter.com/fatego_usa\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Promotional poster FGO game. Sumber gambar: twitter.com/fatego_usa&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/6-22.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/6-22.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-14580 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/6-22.jpg\" alt=\"Fate series fgo english\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-14580\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Promotional poster FGO game. Sumber gambar: twitter.com/fatego_usa</p></div></p>\n<p>Kemudian juga, seperti game-game Fate series lainnya, desain karakter dari game “Fate/Grand Order” juga dibuat menarik dan keren. Karakter yang ada dibuat dengan cantik, ganteng, seksi, serta eye-catching sehingga akan membuat gamer terpikat untuk memainkan game ini.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_14583\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-14583\" data-attachment-id=\"14583\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/fate-series-dari-game-pc-hingga-meraih-popularitas-di-smartphone/attachment/7-65/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/7-16.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Desain karakter yang menarik ‘kan? Sumber gambar: pinterest.com\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/7-16.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/7-16.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-14583 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/7-16.jpg\" alt=\"Fate series scathatch\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-14583\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Desain karakter yang menarik ‘kan? Sumber gambar: pinterest.com</p></div></p>\n<p>Dan jangan lupakan “elemen untung-untungan” alias gacha. Karena bagian ini yang paling bikin kesal/happy dari game Fate/Grand Order buat sebagian gamernya. Gacha System adalah sebuah mekanisme ‘drawing item’. Sebenarnya sistem Gacha ini bukanlah hal baru, karena sudah diterapkan puluhan tahun lalu lewat ‘capsule toys dispenser’ yang banyak terdapat di Jepang. Namun, pada dasarnya sistem ini merupakan sebuah <em>roulette</em> yang mengandalkan nasib baik si pemain game pada saat itu. Sistem ‘Random Number Generator’ akan menentukan apakah gamer Fate/Grand Order akan mendapatkan karakter yang sesuai keinginan mereka, atau malah mendapatkan jenis karakter kelas SSR (alias Super Special Rare), atau bahkan hanya mendapatkan karakter <del>ampas</del>?</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_14568\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-14568\" data-attachment-id=\"14568\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/fate-series-dari-game-pc-hingga-meraih-popularitas-di-smartphone/attachment/2-103/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2-23.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Contoh tampilan GUI di Fate/Grand Order. Sumber gambar: youtube.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Contoh tampilan GUI di Fate/Grand Order. Sumber gambar: youtube.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2-23.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2-23.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-14568 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/2-23.jpg\" alt=\"Fate series fgo crystal\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-14568\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Contoh tampilan GUI di Fate/Grand Order. Sumber gambar: youtube.com</p></div></p>\n<p>Sistem Gacha ini sedang populer; bahkan sering dijadikan lelucon dan meme di berbagai kalangan gamer. Komik online media sosial seperti “Ghosty Comic” misalnya; mereka beberapa kali melakukannya dalam komik mereka.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_14592\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-14592\" data-attachment-id=\"14592\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/fate-series-dari-game-pc-hingga-meraih-popularitas-di-smartphone/attachment/10-38/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/10-7.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Jaret yang mencoba peruntungannya hari itu di gacha. Sumber gambar: ghosty-comic.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Jaret yang mencoba peruntungannya hari itu di gacha. Sumber gambar: ghosty-comic.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/10-7.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/10-7.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-14592 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/10-7.jpg\" alt=\"Fate series ghosty gacha\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-14592\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Jaret yang mencoba peruntungannya hari itu di gacha. Sumber gambar: ghosty-comic.com</p></div></p>\n<p>Jadi intinya, game Fate series mengalami evolusi mulai dari format ‘adult visual novel’ di PC dengan judul “Fate/Stay Night”, hingga saat ini dalam bentuk game RPG Online berjudul “Fate/Grand Order”.</p>\n<p>Tidak hanya dua judul tadi, ada beragam jenis game “Fate” lainnya di luar sana. Dalam berbagai format, dan di berbagai platform. Termasuk manga dan dojinshi. Tema mereka beragam, namun biasanya tetap mengikuti format plot dan karakter populer dari Fate series itu sendiri.</p>\n<p>Seperti Saber, misalnya. Saya pikir dia yang paling populer dan monumental dari serial “Fate” ini.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_14565\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-14565\" data-attachment-id=\"14565\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/fate-series-dari-game-pc-hingga-meraih-popularitas-di-smartphone/attachment/1-139/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/1-33.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Saber dari serial Fate. Sumber gambar: vsbattles.wikia.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Saber dari serial Fate. Sumber gambar: vsbattles.wikia.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/1-33.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/1-33.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-14565 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/1-33.jpg\" alt=\"Fate series saber\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-14565\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Saber dari serial Fate. Sumber gambar: vsbattles.wikia.com</p></div></p>\n<p>Kalau bro sis berminat untuk mulai memasuki dunia game “Fate” series ini, bro sis bisa mulai dari mana saja. Bisa dari ‘adult visual novel’-nya, game console-nya, atau langsung ke yang saat ini populer di kalangan fans: yaitu game RPG Online mobile phone “Fate/Grand Order”. Dan siapkan diri bro sis dalam pertempuran sengit sampai mati di “Holy Grail Wars” antar Masters dengan Servants mereka!</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"cf0ff72a-3240-532d-9963-f105eb9470ed"}}}